GetObjectStoreResponse Model - Response received when fetching an Object Store file.
jobId string
Id of the job, which you can use to request a download URL.
url string
The URL to download the object. This can also be null. To download the object, paste the full URL (including the URL parameters) into a browser.
success boolean
Indicate if the API request was successful.
errors string Array
List of errors with the API call.
